        <a href="/this-week-in-open-source/"
          >actively contributing to a number of open source projects across the Ember Ecosystem,
        </a>
        and our Ember expert Chris Manson is a Member of multiple Ember Core teams and the creator
        of <a href="https://github.com/empress" target="_blank">Empress</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Mainmatter has been developing big web apps and mentored international teams around backend,
        frontend, design, as well as process and developer infrastructure for years. We know what it
